The GC-MS analysis was facilitated by funding through the ICCBS-TWAS Post-Doctoral
Fellowship awarded to Emmanuel Essien and utilized at the H.E.J. Research Institute of Chemistry, International
Centre for Chemical and Biological Sciences (ICCBS), University of Karachi, Karachi, Pakistan.
Emmanuel E. Essien and Paul S. Thomas conceived and designed the experiments;
Paul S. Thomas hydrodistilled the essential oils and performed the antioxidant assays; Emmanuel E. Essien and
Paul S. Thomas wrote the manuscript; Emmanuel E. Essien and Kelly Oriakhi conducted GC/MS analysis and
analyzed the data; Mohammad I. Choudhary supervised the work and provided the GC/MS equipment.
The authors declare no conﬂict of interest.
